                    <td>behaviorstudytools.com, search pages</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td>5-Minute FBA Screener</td>
                    <td>Web tool</td>
                    <td><span class="badge badge-green">10-15%</span></td>
                    <td>Dedicated landing page, social</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td>School BCBA Starter Kit</td>
                    <td>PDF bundle</td>
                    <td><span class="badge badge-yellow">8-12%</span></td>
                    <td>Homepage hero, blog sidebar</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td>Weekly BCBA Brief (newsletter)</td>
                    <td>Email signup</td>
                    <td><span class="badge badge-blue">3-5%</span></td>
                    <td>Blog footer, about page</td>
                </tr>
            </tbody>
        </table>

        <h3>Form Copy</h3>
        <p><strong>Headline:</strong> "Join 500+ BCBAs who get one actionable tip every Tuesday"</p>
        <p><strong>Button:</strong> "Send me the tips" (not "Subscribe")</p>
        <p><strong>Fields:</strong> Email only (collect name in welcome sequence)</p>
    </div>

    <!-- Timing -->
    <div class="section-card">
        <h2>📅 Send Schedule</h2>
        <table>
            <thead>
                <tr>
                    <th>Period</th>
                    <th>Frequency</th>
                    <th>Time</th>
                </tr>
            </thead>
            <tbody>
                <tr>
                    <td>School year (Sep-Jun)</td>
                    <td>Weekly</td>
                    <td>Tuesday 6:30 AM PT / 9:30 AM ET</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td>Summer (Jul-Aug)</td>
                    <td>Biweekly</td>
                    <td>Career/professional content focus</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td>Holiday weeks</td>
                    <td>Skip</td>
                    <td>Thanksgiving, winter break, spring break</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td>BACB exam windows</td>
                    <td>2x/week</td>
                    <td>Exam-focused content (temporary)</td>
                </tr>
            </tbody>
        </table>

        <h3>Why Tuesday 6:30 AM PT?</h3>
        <ul>
            <li>Tuesday/Wednesday are top B2B days (Monday = IEP meetings)</li>
            <li>9:30 AM ET hits morning scan window for largest timezone clusters</li>
            <li>Avoids 8 AM crush of school system notifications</li>
            <li>A/B test against 3:30 PM ET (after-school) in Phase 2</li>
        </ul>
    </div>

    <!-- Segmentation -->
    <div class="section-card">
        <h2>🏷️ Segmentation Model</h2>
        <table>
            <thead>
                <tr>
                    <th>Segment</th>
                    <th>Criteria</th>
                    <th>Content Adjustment</th>
                </tr>
            </thead>
            <tbody>
                <tr>
                    <td>Role: BCBA</td>
                    <td>Self-reported</td>
                    <td>Full newsletter content</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td>Role: RBT</td>
                    <td>Self-reported</td>
                    <td>Simpler language, implementation focus</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td>Role: Student/Candidate</td>
                    <td>Self-reported</td>
                    <td>Add exam prep, study tips</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td>Active (60 days)</td>
                    <td>Opened or clicked in last 60 days</td>
                    <td>Standard sends</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td>Cooling (60-90 days)</td>
                    <td>No opens in 60-90 days</td>
                    <td>Re-engagement sequence</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td>Cold (90+ days)</td>
                    <td>No opens in 90+ days</td>
                    <td>Sunset sequence, then suppress</td>
                </tr>
            </tbody>
        </table>
    </div>

    <!-- Re-engagement -->
    <div class="section-card">
        <h2>🔄 Re-engagement Sequence (60-90 day inactive)</h2>
        <div class="email-sequence">
            <div class="email-card">
                <div class="day">Email 1</div>
                <div class="subject">Subject: Still interested? Here's what you've missed</div>
                <div class="outline">Curated best-of content from the last few months</div>
            </div>
            <div class="email-card">
                <div class="day">Email 2 — 7 days later</div>
                <div class="subject">Subject: Should I stop sending these?</div>
                <div class="outline">Direct and honest. Give them an easy out or a reason to stay.</div>
            </div>
            <div class="email-card">
                <div class="day">Email 3 — 7 days later (if no engagement)</div>
                <div class="subject">Subject: This is your last email from us</div>
                <div class="outline">Auto-suppress after this. Protects sender reputation.</div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- List Hygiene -->
    <div class="section-card">
        <h2>🧹 List Hygiene Protocol</h2>
        
        <h3>Ongoing (Automated)</h3>
        <ul>
            <li>Remove hard bounces immediately</li>
            <li>Suppress soft bounces after 3 consecutive failures</li>
            <li>Flag spam complaints for immediate removal</li>
            <li>Verify new emails at capture (real-time validation)</li>
        </ul>

        <h3>Monthly</h3>
        <ul>
            <li>Review bounce rate (target: under 2%)</li>
            <li>Review spam complaint rate (target: under 0.1%)</li>
            <li>Identify cold subscribers (no engagement 90 days)</li>
        </ul>

        <h3>Quarterly</h3>
        <ul>
            <li>Run re-engagement campaign for cooling segment</li>
            <li>Sunset cold subscribers who don't re-engage</li>
            <li>Audit segment definitions</li>
            <li>Clean duplicate records</li>
        </ul>
    </div>

</div>

<script>
function copyTemplate(id) {
    const text = document.getElementById(id).innerText;
    navigator.clipboard.writeText(text).then(() => {
        const btn = event.target;
        btn.innerText = 'Copied!';
        setTimeout(() => btn.innerText = 'Copy Template', 2000);
    });
}
</script>
